data.name: AboutButton.ToolTip
data.value: Show the about and copyright dialog.

data.name: QuickFirstFailingByteMethodCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: If a failure is encountered, skip testing all written files from the beginning. Search for the last successful byte in reverse instead. (recommended)

data.name: QuickTestAfterEachFileCheckBox.Text
data.value: Quick test after writing each GiB of test data

data.name: QuickTestAfterEachFileCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Performs brief spot checks as data is written. Enabling this will detect common failures much faster. (recommended)

data.name: RemoveTempDataFilesButton.ToolTip
data.value: Only files created by MediaTester will be removed.

data.name: RemoveTempDataFilesUponCompletionCheckBox.Text
data.value: Remove temp data files upon completion

data.name: RemoveTempDataFilesUponCompletionCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Remove temporary data files after verification completion (pass or fail).

data.name: SaveOptionsButton.ToolTip
data.value: Save current options as deafults for next launch.

data.name: SaveTestResultsFileToMediaCheckBox.Text
data.value: Save test results file to media root

data.name: SaveTestResultsFileToMediaCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Save test results file to media with full test log output. MediaTesterResults_YYYY-MM-DD_hh-mm-ss.txt Temp test data files will be removed, if necessary, to create space for the test results file.

data.name: StopProcessingOnFailureCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Stop the test process after a single failure. (recommended)

data.name: VerifyOnlyButton.ToolTip
data.value: Verify previous written test data. Will not write anything to media.

data.name: WriteAndVerifyButton.ToolTip
data.value: Write test data to media then read back to verify data was stored correctly. Only available space will be used. Non-destructive.
